  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-CON-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package was signed at initial submission; one mesh-refinement validation result was subsequently appended without re-signing, introducing a future-dated evidence item (W-CON-03). The narrative notes the package was 'updated post-signing' to include the supplemental mesh study but the signatureTimestamp was not refreshed.",
